</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:22
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='731929' id='t-731929'>In conclusion, what can you do today?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='734836' id='t-734836'>Now, tweets, who's tweeting?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='740060' id='t-740060'>Please, I beg of you,
