<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='770724' id='t-770724'>That's the first thing we can do.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:03
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='772896' id='t-772896'>Second, there are many other things
