<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='812813' id='t-812813'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='823980' id='t-823980'>Let's get rid of this cultural cringe.</span>
</span>
</p>
